GOVERNMENT OF INDIA
CABINET SECRETARIAT
(Department of Cabinet Affairs)
New Delhi, the 1st September, 1970.
10th Bhadra, 1892.
The undersigned is directed to state that with
effect from the afternoon of August 31, 1970, Shri Bharru Prakash Singh
relinquished the office of Doputy Minister in the Ministry of
Petroleum, and Chemicals and Mines & Motals.
(R.N. Kalia)

Secretary to the Vice-President, for information.
